data.description: Location, location, location! Welcome to this 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath, home near Hershey in Derry Township School District.  Southpoint  2 story located not far from major highway accesses, the Harrisburg airport , Harrisburg Capitol & downtown Hershey. Spacious living room, large formal dining room, eat-in kitchen with granite counters & TV hook-up, 1st floor laundry room, and family room with wood burning fireplace. Sliders in family room lead to deck and backyard with gorgeous in-ground swimming pool, great for summertime fun! Upstairs there are 4 bedrooms; two of the 4 bedrooms are primary suites with private baths, large walk-in closets, ceiling fans and showers. Two more spacious bedrooms with ceiling fans & the 3rd full bath has a tub/shower combo. So much to offer! Corner lot, shed, fenced backyard and side entry 2 car garage. Add your own updates & personality to this home and make it  yours today!
